Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pirates who are after the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...head for the New World, the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew reached Fishman Island located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,where the New Fishman Pirates who are looking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after Shirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats find themselves caught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--Mother-sama! --Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Otohime-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Otohime...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust the woman who you chose to be your wife
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty! Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:27.38,B1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"A Sudden Tragedy! A Gunshot Shuts Down the Future!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Otohime's voyage was to determine the fate of Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, we were all worrying but it was nothing compared to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the burden of the Neptune family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole Ryugu Kingdom was restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But all we could do was pray for the Queen's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A Tamate Box?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:05:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Captain. I heard that they have one at the Ryugu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And it makes anyone grow older?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, a small brat like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...would become a sexy mature woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Problem solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I can get married to Shirahoshi right away, I suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Go steal that Tamate Box thing now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. There is no way to break in to the Ryugu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,--But if you get married to Shirahoshi first... --You can go in and out as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi is not bad-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If she grows older by 10 to 20 years, she will be really hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But she'll get even bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll look just fine! I like big women!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:06:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the legendary Mermaid Princess who can control the Sea Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When I become her husband and seize that power,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,our dream will come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the dream of all the ancestors of Vander Decken family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll start writing an invitation to our wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to propose to her first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't have any friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There had been no word from the Queen for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:32.11,OS,,0,0,0,,WE NEED YOUR SIGNATURE FOR THE FUTURE OF THE ISLAND!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And worries kept growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna hear her speeches again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come back safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss. Where is Otohime-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When will she come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep faith in her and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She embarked on a voyage to make the future better for you kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:07:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, please be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She will be fine-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's trust in her and wait-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That one week felt like 100 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We are so happy just to see you alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,After a few days of convincing, Queen Otohime finally succeeded...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...in calming down the Celestial Dragons and she brought back with her a sheet of paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...which held the fate of Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,CONCHCORDE PLAZA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, the World Nobles are very influential...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the World Summit - the Summit of Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to what they wrote on this sheet of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"To foster friendship between the Fishmen and humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,we will pledge our endorsement of their duly signed petition."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That means if we can submit a petition with many signatures at the Summit,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,this one sheet of paper will give us all the support we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can relocate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,--The Celestial Dragons will support the petition? --I have mixed feelings about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So what I need now is more signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can do is wait for you to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Express your intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...to relocate to the world above and live together with the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your signature!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You children, you aren't going to go back on your pledge after raising my hopes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't! My mom said she will sign too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Otohime-sama, this small box won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know the population of this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here, here! Put them in here from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who support the Queen's passion, put your signature in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fishmen and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We were trying to ignore the history of racism.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Queen took the first step herself and now we have hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If she can get enough signatures, the future of the island could change for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:12:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have helped Arlong if he could have understood better...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...about Queen Otohime's firm belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish Brother Tai were here to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother! Signatures keep coming in from all over the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's going well, isn't it? --Yes, it's like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of your courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I got encouraged at that very moment, that this island would change for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the moment that the Sea Kings came and stared at the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That was surprising!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi called them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We Merfolk can communicate with fish and talk to them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:13:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one can talk to those great Sea Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even your father Neptune who can talk to whales, doesn't know how to talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But according to our royal family's legend, once in several hundred years,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,one with an ability to communicate with the Sea Kings, will be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,--With those giant Sea Kings?! --And Shirahoshi is the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and she will meet someone who will guide her and her power in the right direction
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and it will cause a major change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's true, there will be a major change on this island too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it help what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it could.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a power of love that can save thousands of lives if only the bearer wishes to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But with the wrong intentions, that power could sink the whole world into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It is one of the most fearsome powers in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi doesn't know that she has that power and she doesn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,how to control it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If something were ever to shock her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,she could unintentionally drive the Sea Kings berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishman Island would be flattened like a pancake! What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I can take care of it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But the three of you will have to become strong warriors someday
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and as her brothers and as warriors,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,protect your baby sister with your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yes! --Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But then the unexpected happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Signatures were mounting up at a rapid pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The islanders still didn't trust humans
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but they were hoping to see the beginning of a new era.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought our signatures again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's against the rules! Each person can only vote once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it means a lot to me that you did so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your efforts finally paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,--How could the box catch fire? --Water! Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Put out the fire now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The signatures we collected!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Put out the fire! We have to save the signatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They are very important! I have to save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let them burn! They are everyone's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the future of Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Save the signatures now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save yourself! Leave the rest up to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Otohime-sama has been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The shooter must be here somewhere! Protect the royal family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,--Mother! --Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous here! Get on the gondola now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Princes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty! Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,--Your Majesty! --Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, Princess, this is pretty serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,--Who're you?! --Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,--Stay away from the Princess! --Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--Mother-sama! Mother! --Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Who the hell did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,--Didn't an emergency team arrive yet?! --Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be forgiven! I'll make him pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay near me, my angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose your temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My guard was down. Because I was thrilled that everybody was signing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Fukaboshi, I should be the one who is frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, you need treatment now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't matter who did this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get angry on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let resentment or hatred get the better of you for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mother-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi, keep your senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If something were ever to shock her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just like...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Moonfish mambo! Moonfish mambo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Moonfish mambo! Moonfish mambo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Moonfish mambo! Moonfish mambo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's fun! It's fun! --Shake, shake! Shake, shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's nothing! Let's sing Shirahoshi! --Moonfish mambo! Shake, shake, shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We three will always be there for you-la-ti-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mambo dance is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun-do-re-mi-fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Princes, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,--Stop them! --That's not appropriate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, look, we're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We will protect our baby sister like this forever-la-ti-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Can't you see the Queen's situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We will collect the signatures that burned away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We three will become great warriors like our father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...and protect Shirahoshi with our lives as we promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.11,0:21:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We are almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.63,0:22:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,At that place under the real sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,After Otohime's death, Fishman Island is consumed by rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.72,0:23:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the end for her ideal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After relating the subsequent events on Fishman Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and finishing his story, Jinbe again apologizes to Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.83,0:23:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nami's reply was utterly unexpected!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.70,0:23:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"Back to the Present! Hody Makes a Move!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.77,0:23:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
